# Generated by third_party/gmp-wasm/README.md's build recipe, not
# vendored — regenerate locally when building the wasm target (gmp.h is
# partially generated by GMP's own configure step, so it's build output
# too, not pure source, same reasoning as the .a libs below it).
third_party/gmp-wasm/include/
third_party/gmp-wasm/lib/

# Assembled by packages/kex/scripts/build.sh from build-wasm/ — build
# output, not source, same reasoning as the gmp-wasm entries above.
packages/kex/dist/
